{"tid":1653858,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]城市遊擊, 首要隱密低調, 唔好咁on9話俾人知你幾時去遍地開花","createTime":"2019-10-14T09:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T13:34:52.000Z","uid":198175,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"947158a921d788f8a0a96469304d6b2044b6ff10","tid":1653858,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"陣地戰不敵, 先轉去打遊擊, 就係為咗避免與敵方正面接觸對抗, 以最少的兵力及代價去達成戰略目的, 唔止係敵後騷擾咁簡單.<br />\n<br />\n所以邊會有咁on9早幾日就公佈全世界你邊日幾點至幾點出嚟, 連有乜目標都俾對方知道晒, 讓對方以逸待勞部署重兵就位埋伏, 變相自投羅網.<br />\n<br />\n打遊擊, 係在己方地盤敵後對抗佔領軍, 隱密低調, 藏鳥於林, 攻其不備, 防不勝防, 措手不及, 打完即閃, 有若行雲流水, 不佔領不戀戰, 咁先有得長有長玩.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d038f2e396e7af44ec08441fd93429d43dbb50","tid":1653858,"uid":27647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364d1917f71ec582a1d13e2a5687e018387a62d6","tid":1653858,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"講完都冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n總之唔好阻人返工"},{"pid":"1c1b296cbf7bfdbbae9fc16b6fa066f5b6941102","tid":1653858,"uid":63464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"以成積論，大遊行嘅裝修好像好d,不過2樣都有就最好"},{"pid":"62ed12ab528198dd927c98e6e37743e06a444436","tid":1653858,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"打遊擊係唔會打敗敵軍，但打遊擊所達成的戰略成果足以影響大局，甚至迫敵軍退讓或提出休戰，最終達至最終勝利。"},{"pid":"35c46e22a4094c2d8a416ada17b9e70152b45c84","tid":1653858,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca12cb9ad9a62de44a4bf82f8cec9db759a2167","tid":1653858,"uid":198175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c1b296cbf7bfdbbae9fc16b6fa066f5b6941102","tid":1653858,"uid":63464,"like":0,"disl